Please bring the girl we met
in Torigo, mo. We'll be waiting
at the concert venue, mo.

rows.label: qst201623_msg0002
rows.name:
Since our words aren't
reaching Nanakoori-san,
she's our only hope, mo.

rows.label: qst201625_msg0102
rows.name:
Now, please let her see
Nanakoori-san quickly, mo.
